N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 11 ยง 29.2 - Applicability

State Regulations

This Part shall apply to any licensee who receives from a governmental unit, insurer or other licensee a fee and/or commission, or part thereof, in connection with insurance services rendered to, and/or insurance coverages placed or renewed for, any governmental unit in this State. Notes
